{"tid":644479,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"世界人口50億，係咪最理想？","createTime":"2018-04-27T09:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T09:59:18.000Z","uid":149978,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5065c52cfe9a72ad9dcc300c512b40b80bc5b4","tid":644479,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:08:17.000Z","msg":"邊度樓價收入比最平？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.numbeo.com/property-investment/rankings.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.numbeo.com%2Fproperty-investment%2Frankings.jsp&d=ZYVhrGFvApibtd1c5U7j4R4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=24a68b72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.numbeo.com/property-investment/rankings.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n絕大部分都係美國的城市。<br />\n<br />\n美國，如果肯做埋槍械管制，冇咁多人持槍，冇咁多槍擊案，基本上係世界上最完美的國家。美國是地上最強科學研究，最強科技，最強經濟，最強軍事國。自然環境也很好，很理想。美國農業也係全球生產量最高的國家之一。<br />\n<br />\n中國和印度人口多，城市樓價自然貴。<br />\n<br />\n加拿大、澳洲、蒙古、新西蘭人口密度低，但樓價收入比一樣偏高。可能因為唔夠人力資源起樓，同埋可能因為唔夠人，所以令發展要變得太集中。<br />\n<br />\n如果世界好似美國人口密度（每平方公里34人），咁世界人口就係50億。<br />\n<br />\n其實美國係咪已經證明左，50億人係最理想？<br />\n<br />\n按此推論，中國理想人口是4億至5億人左右。印度理想人口都係3億至4億人左右。"},{"pid":"b67684961c3c41b2b70894bde18836260b33c493","tid":644479,"uid":56824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:31:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b469302f8f418de88e9807b57d8a481f46250d55","tid":644479,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:56:43.000Z","msg":"共濟會話係5億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cee88c04dd7d2732a8ff27fb7ed85a41c73117","tid":644479,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b67684961c3c41b2b70894bde18836260b33c493","tid":644479,"uid":56824,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:31:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"唔需要。<br />\n叫政府繼續不鼓勵生育就可以。<br />\n<br />\n唔好現在咁快就學新加坡/當